<div style="margin: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><h4>Daria Thompson</h4><a href="https://github.com/dariathompson"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a></div>

<div style="margin: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><h4>Nima Soufiani</h4><a href="https://github.com/nimzyow"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a></div>

<div style="margin: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><h4>Anton Plisnier</h4><a href="https://github.com/apliz"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a></div>

<div style="margin: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><h4>Lila Walker</h4><a href="https://github.com/lilawalker"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a></div>

<div style="margin: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;"><h4>John Baxter</h4><a href="https://github.com/john-baxter"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a></div>

</div>
